title: Clever Eleven Jan. 2008
description:
The first month of the new year has passed and produced some big tunes from lesser names, while the more established acts obviously hold their cards tight until springtime. 

1. Clocks - All I Can
2. The Little Ones - Ordinary Song
3. Morrissey - That&#039;s How People Grow Up
4. Nada Surf - Whose Authority
5. Lightspeed Champion - Tell Me What Its Worth
6. Mexicolas - Easy Smile
7. Bob Mould - The Silence Between Us
8. Matt Costa - Emergency Call
9. The Whigs - Hot Bed
10. The Magnetic Fields - California Girls
11. One Night Only - Just For Tonight
